'''特莱平原'''（{{lang-hi|तराई}}；{{lang-ne|तराइ}}；{{lang-en|Terai}}，印地语和尼泊尔语中意为“湿谷，山脚低地”<ref>{{cite book |author1=Ronald Stuart McGregor |title=The Oxford Hindi-English Dictionary |date=1993 |publisher=Oxford University Press |location=London |isbn=9780198643395 |page=441 |url=https://dsal.uchicago.edu/cgi-bin/app/mcgregor_query.py?page=441 |accessdate=2021-08-22 |archive-date=2021-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210822065413/https://dsal.uchicago.edu/cgi-bin/app/mcgregor_query.py?page=441 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |author1=Sir Ralph Lilley Turner |title=A comparative dictionary of Indo-Aryan languages |date=1962-1966 |publisher=Oxford University Press |location=London |isbn=9788120816657 |page=324 |url=https://dsal.uchicago.edu/cgi-bin/app/soas_query.py?page=324 |accessdate=2021-08-22 |archive-date=2021-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210822060905/https://dsal.uchicago.edu/cgi-bin/app/soas_query.py?page=324 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |author1=John Thompson Platts |title=A dictionary of Urdu, classical Hindi, and English |date=1884 |publisher=W. H. Allen & Co. |location=London |isbn=9781497907805 |page=316 |url=https://dsal.uchicago.edu/cgi-bin/app/platts_query.py?page=316 |accessdate=2021-08-22 |archive-date=2021-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211116234533/https://dsal.uchicago.edu/cgi-bin/app/platts_query.py?page=316 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |author1=Sir Ralph Lilley Turner |title=A comparative and etymological dictionary of the Nepali language |date=1931 |publisher=K. Paul, Trench, Trubner |location=London |isbn=9788183630115 |page=274 |url=https://dsal.uchicago.edu/cgi-bin/app/turnernepali_query.py?page=274 |accessdate=2021-08-22 |archive-date=2021-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210822060905/https://dsal.uchicago.edu/cgi-bin/app/turnernepali_query.py?page=274 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |author1=Ruth Laila Schmidt |title=A Practical dictionary of modern Nepali |date=1994 |publisher=Ratna Sagar |isbn=9788170701729 |page=277 |url=https://dsal.uchicago.edu/cgi-bin/app/schmidt_query.py?page=277 |accessdate=2021-08-22 |archive-date=2021-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210822060906/https://dsal.uchicago.edu/cgi-bin/app/schmidt_query.py?page=277 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |author1=S. W. Fallon |title=A new Hindustani-English dictionary, with illustrations from Hindustani literature and folk-lore |date=1879 |publisher=Trubner and Co. |location=London |isbn=9788120603738 |page=408 |url=https://dsal.uchicago.edu/cgi-bin/app/fallon_query.py?page=408 |accessdate=2021-08-22 |archive-date=2021-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210822065410/https://dsal.uchicago.edu/cgi-bin/app/fallon_query.py?page=408 |dead-url=no }}</ref>），也译作'''德赖平原'''，是[[印度河-恒河平原|印度河-恒河平原]]北部的[[尼泊尔|尼泊尔]]-[[印度|印度]]交界处的一处低地地区。北靠[[喜马拉雅山脉|喜马拉雅山脉]]及[[西瓦利克山脉|西瓦利克山脉]]。该地区主要为[[草原|草原]]、[[疏林草原|疏林草原]]、[[娑罗树|娑罗树]]林及[[沼泽|沼泽]]组成。海拔在60-300米左右。为[[亚热带|亚热带]]气候。

[[奇特旺国家公园|奇特旺国家公园]]及[[巴尔迪亚国家公园|巴尔迪亚国家公园]]（Bardiya National Park）位于该区域。這里以前主要居民是[[塔魯族|塔魯族]]，在根除瘧疾後中部丘陵地區民族大舉南下，[[巴洪|巴洪]]和[[切特里|切特里]]也成為主要居民。

英语中的{{link-en|特赖帽|terai hat}}（阔边毡帽）即得名于此。<ref>{{cite book |title=The Oxford English Dictionary, Volume 17 |publisher=Clarendon Press |isbn=9780198611868 |page=794 |edition=2, reprint}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=terai hat |url=https://www.dictionary.com/browse/terai-hat |website=Dictionary.com BASED ON THE RANDOM HOUSE UNABRIDGED DICTIONARY, © RANDOM HOUSE, INC. |accessdate=2021-08-22 |archive-date=2021-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210822062729/https://www.dictionary.com/browse/terai-hat |dead-url=no }}</ref>


